{"tid":1657123,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發]黨鐵又出意外,撞車","createTime":"2019-10-16T02:45:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T04:33:18.000Z","uid":196751,"like":25,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"c2f0194ef0adcd3fa0571de44ad3b663066f7c90","tid":1657123,"uid":196751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T02:45:39.000Z","msg":"十日前突發,點解無晒聲氣? <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/f1j518X.jpg\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/92QQBHs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F92QQBHs.jpg&h=f42fa33e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wxNrUt6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwxNrUt6.jpg&h=f4270847&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/OsXWoPN.png\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0LmMofh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0LmMofh.jpg&h=7ee5fdef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n出軌呢?<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0xns2F2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0xns2F2.jpg&h=be5aa8e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n沙中線偷工減料已經好嚴重<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xejK4Vc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxejK4Vc.jpg&h=966cd7c2&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n城大種下草都冧天花,如果上面係幾百幾千噸大廈,海水會點?<br />\n而問題係城大冧天花竟然不提告<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MgNAr9m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMgNAr9m.jpg&h=2529dbf3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n撞車唔係少事,出軌同撞車真係可以死好多人,今次無人死只係咁好彩<br />\n大家都唔希望下一個係你或者你珍惜既人<br />\n市民應該追究到底 ,黨鐵應該有高層下台,無理由只係罰車長<br />\n仲有作為大股東既政府都應該負責<br />\n<br />\n國際鐵路出軌撞車事故<br />\n14/7/2013 巴黎火車撞月台6死200傷<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mJ3oA4F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmJ3oA4F.jpg&h=a4870c07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n9/9/2016 西班牙火車出軌意外至少4死47傷<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/03Cs2Js.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F03Cs2Js.jpg&h=61836d90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n20/11/2016 印度火車出軌翻覆至少91人死亡逾百人傷<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RNqydQf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRNqydQf.jpg&h=4591df1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n21/10/2018 台灣列車翻覆意外8節全出軌18死近200人傷<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8umhFvw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8umhFvw.jpg&h=80886e67&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"419c8d2db2c86fdc47e0c1830c7409742e1db1ac","tid":1657123,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T02:45:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zBif5mg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzBif5mg.jpg&h=44757529&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"680df9fb9d673eb80b895d6423e5d0cb1774f310","tid":1657123,"uid":196751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T02:46:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9364d74bfaff8b9666b4744b6336a5104912d8e","tid":1657123,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T02:46:48.000Z","msg":"有野想捐可以FB搵我地香港自由之書阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">係呀,我知我地講近廢話,但前線的確需要支援</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1655137/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1655137/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\nFB: 國難五金, 香港自由之書"},{"pid":"abfba9cb4462e562a496caadc9f5154401acd80d","tid":1657123,"uid":263944,"like":0,"dislike":0